            Our high-volume locations offer your coupon deals to well over 500,000 annually.
            Our kiosks are impressive and demand attention as they stand 6.5 feet high and include a 42” touchscreen to navigate to the coupons of choice. The customer selects the coupons of interest and they are sent out for their immediate use.
        </p>
